[UPCOMING] - XXXX-XX-XX
***********************

Bug fixes:

- Calculation of the allelic covariance matrix in calc.covariance was found to
  incorrectly use the sample covariance instead of the population covariance,
  which could lead to non-positive-definite covariance matrices in rare cases
  with small sample sizes. (@petrelharp, PR #34)

